WEBVTT

56:13.964 --> 56:15.173
You insulted me.

56:15.839 --> 56:16.964
You have insulted me very badly.

56:17.423 --> 56:18.048
I'll go.

56:18.714 --> 56:21.006
I'll leave.
-Shankar… Listen to me.

56:21.006 --> 56:22.839
I'll go home. Enough of your insults.
-Listen to me.

56:23.089 --> 56:24.714
I'll leave. I don't want you.
-Shankar, listen to me.

56:29.881 --> 56:30.464
Madam…

56:31.048 --> 56:32.339
He's very dangerous.

56:33.464 --> 56:35.839
He has planned a grand scheme
and entered the girl’s house.

56:36.964 --> 56:38.839
I'm nervous about what he might do to that girl.

56:39.173 --> 56:41.006
Idiot. Why do you care about the girl?
